<para0><title>Major Paragraph Title</title>
<para>Textual information in 5 by 8 inch manuals shall be presented
on the left-hand page and the related illustration on the right-hand
page.  Textual information for standard size 8&frac12; by 11 inch
manuals shall be presented in double column format with textual information
located at the top half of the page and the related illustration on
the bottom.</para>
